added example-weights
from the stc user fork: https://github.com/stc/ofxColorQuantizer/
This example can sort colors weighted based on their areas, their order is based on their chroma values.

added example-weights2
This current fork has another example that can sort by Hue, Saturation, Brightness or the above one.
It has a gui too to change the number of colors, the sorting type, etc on the fly.
There's some image loading from url too.

![alt text](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/moebiussurfing/ofxColorQuantizer/master/screenshots/screenshot1.png)

